<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在要怎么办？”悟空大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“独角兕大王吸走了我们的兵器！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天兵摸了摸自己的下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去非常严肃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不能就这样回天庭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果玉帝知道我们没有抓住那个妖怪的话，他会生气的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”火神说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要再想个别的办法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在天快黑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了晚上的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们中的一个人可以溜进洞里去把那金钢圈偷出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雷神笑了。“我知道谁最适合干这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都看向雷神。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们当中有一个神偷。”雷神继续说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他曾经偷了蟠桃园里的所有蟠桃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，所有人都看向悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空假笑了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，确实如此。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我以前是偷过东西，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我现在知道偷东西是不对的了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我还是会去偷那金钢圈的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我得救唐僧。你们在这里等我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成了一只小虫子，飞进了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他飞过一条又一条长长的黑暗隧道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他听到了独角兕大王的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空顺着声音飞了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那妖怪正坐在床边自言自语，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手臂上依然戴着那金钢圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“该睡觉了。”妖怪打了个哈欠说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望明天可以吃了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天没吃成，就是因为那只讨厌的猴子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪躺下，很快就睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞了过去，落在妖怪的手臂上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要在他的手臂上咬几口。”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他觉得痒的话，就会把金钢圈拿下来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空在妖怪的手臂上咬了一口又一口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪翻了个身，说着梦话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“臭虫......痒......”他挠了挠手臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又咬了几口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪又挠了挠，但他还是没有把金钢圈拿下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这方法没用。”悟空想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正要离开的时候，突然发现了墙角里有一些东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大吃一惊。“我们的兵器！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地变回了原形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把金箍棒变小后放入耳朵里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后拿起了火矛、雷电，还有宝剑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞穴外，其他人都在等着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天兵握紧了拳头说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望悟空可以把金钢圈偷出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我实在是太生气了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”火神说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他居然吸走了我的火矛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雷神举起一只手说：“嘘。门开了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们屏住了呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们看见悟空出来的时候，都松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你拿到那个金钢圈了吗？”雷神问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，但是你们看！”悟空举起了那些兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“干得好，悟空！”火神说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雷神拍了下悟空的背。“谢谢你，悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天兵举起了他的宝剑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有兵器了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在可以轻松地打败那个妖怪了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看大家。“大家都准备好了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好了！”天兵说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好了！”火神说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好了！”雷神说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用力敲着洞门喊道：“醒醒，独角兕大王！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马上出来，不然我们就毁了你的山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪走到了外面，打着哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他看到兵器的时候说道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们居然敢从我这里偷东西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起了金钢圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在大家还没有反应过来的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些兵器又一次被吸进了金钢圈里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>